{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 53,
  "title": "第五十三章（益證）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "使我介然有知，行於大道。"
    },
    {
      "text": "唯施是畏。"
    },
    {
      "text": "大道甚夷，而民好徑。"
    },
    {
      "text": "朝甚除，"
    },
    {
      "text": "田甚蕪，"
    },
    {
      "text": "倉甚虛，"
    },
    {
      "text": "服文綵，"
    },
    {
      "text": "帶利劍，"
    },
    {
      "text": "厭飲食，財貨有餘，"
    },
    {
      "text": "是謂盜誇。"
    },
    {
      "text": "非道哉。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "介，大也。老子疾時王不行大道，故設此言。使我介然有知於政事，我則行於大道，躬行無為之化。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "唯，獨也。獨畏有所施為，恐失道意。欲賞善，恐偽善生；欲信忠，恐詐忠起。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夷，平易也。徑，邪、不平正也。大道甚平易，而民好從邪徑也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "高台榭，宮室修。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "農事廢，不耕治。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "五穀傷害，國無儲也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "好飾偽，貴外華。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "尚剛強，武且奢。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "多嗜欲，無足時。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "百姓而君有餘者，是由劫盜以為服飾，持行誇人，不知身死家破，親戚並隨也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人君所行如是，此非道也。復言也哉者，痛傷之辭。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
